@startuml US-03
title US-03 Browse All Games

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "GameController" as GC
control "GameService" as GS
database "GameRepository" as GR

User -> UI: Open Home Page
UI -> GC: GET /games
GC -> GS: listGames()
GS -> GR: findAll()
GR --> GS: games(title, price)
GS --> GC: games
GC --> UI: 200 OK + list
UI --> User: Render game cards
@enduml
